g.title: j987002302
g.text: So, what's the situation with the metal cranes you make?

g.title: j2976851656
g.text: Would you be willing to make me a metal crane?

g.title: j3749500860
g.text: they're pretty! and fun! most importantly...

g.title: j1448607742
g.text: I suppoooose I would, but they're really for me ;)

g.title: j3442867888
g.text: You seem upset. Is it something I said?

g.title: j1967990901
g.text: I thought that was for *paper* cranes.

g.title: j2021158314
g.text: What? Where did you hear that?

g.title: j1629489338
g.text: oh yes but *metal* cranes are even more magical (I like to think)

g.title: j2892895345
g.text: I thought it was common knowledge!

g.title: j2011749460
g.text: I didn't love being called boring.

g.title: j3881915566
g.text: I've never heard that in my life.

g.title: j2181323471
g.text: First I'm hearing of this. I'd love to know more.

g.title: j1309977723
g.text: Actually, come to think of it, I think I did hear that once.

g.title: j3766896613
g.text: That doesn't sound real, but if it makes you happy, that's cool.

g.title: j1619087230
g.text: Oh. I really didn't mean anything by it.

g.title: j3960522359
g.text: I'm sure! cranes have a proven track record, u know

g.title: j268468359
g.text: wasn't too ridiculous for the Jipangu space program!

g.title: j3105159870
g.text: then allow me to fill u in ^_^

g.title: j292954942
g.text: before Jipangu trained their astronauts to go to space, they had candidates fold 1000 cranes. true story!

g.title: j2926494440
g.text: it's just what it sounds like! when u fold 1000 cranes, ur supposed to get a wish. traditionally, people fold paper, but I'm sure folding metal works just as well lol

g.title: j2108252654
g.text: allow me to grant ur wish ;)

g.title: j2650504552
g.text: oh excellent! who couldn't use a wish, right? it's a lovely notion

g.title: j1046735978
g.text: So, how many have you folded by now?

g.title: j3159416093
g.text: I've seen you fold a lot. Have you gotten to 1000 before?

g.title: j1985420798
g.text: Honest. I'm sorry I upset you.

g.title: j893550012
g.text: You're not boring, Aoi. I just thought I was being clever.

g.title: j3174808875
g.text: If you were really boring, I wouldn't be talking to you.

g.title: j3693409908
g.text: I doubt that was because of some superstition. They were probably just testing concentration or something like that.

g.title: j4253045941
g.text: Ah, interesting. Skill-testing and luck-building all in one. Very wise.

g.title: j962785949
g.text: a few hundred. I have a tally tucked away somewhere between all my CDs lol

g.title: j1772204864
g.text: actually yes! that wish wasn't for me though. time I get a wish for myself, dontcha think?

g.title: j165823094
g.text: It seems the jury's convinced by your defense

g.title: j1227134530
g.text: How do you not have a precise number? I thought you'd have that memorized haha

g.title: j902155758
g.text: Oh yeah? What lucky someone got that wish?

g.title: j1411075754
g.text: and grants you a fresh start

g.title: j3424053112
g.text: no way! focusing on the end is just overwhelming. the trick is to focus on the moment. one step at a time! then one day u look around and go "oh look at that I'm done" ^_^

g.title: j4129944096
g.text: if I tell u, it won't come tru!

g.title: j1613125563
g.text: weeeell it's not a very cheery tale. I'd rather not get into it right now.

g.title: j4275202473
g.text: cranes don't have to be metal. go on, start folding that paper! ^_^ or metal, if u prefer! (tho I think u'll find that much harder)

g.title: j2846531316
g.text: I don't mean that as a bad thing.

g.title: j1321743139
g.text: Ah, so you're pacing yourself. I guess I can see how raw numbers can take away from the creativity.

g.title: j3385549038
g.text: My mistake! I should have thought of that. Be sure not to tell me!

g.title: j2775124081
g.text: I don't think that rule applies to wishes made of metal and paper.

g.title: j1369410731
g.text: Oh. Hey, I'm sorry to hear that.

g.title: j165497326
g.text: Are you sure? I'd really like to hear it.

g.title: j509263507
g.text: But I want YOU to make my cranes.

g.title: j654668171
g.text: Oh, I see Aoi's emoticons are back. I think that's a good sign.

g.title: j2771981643
g.text: so like did u just ask about my cranes to make fun of me ooor... ?

g.title: j3730976770
g.text: gosh my whole "these cranes are a deeply personal symbol of growth for me and take a heck of a lot of time to make" thing went right over ur head, huh?

g.title: j2776544888
g.text: I couldn't have said it better! ^_^

g.title: j2234590622
g.text: well, the good news is when u fold ur 1000 cranes, u can track them however u want!

g.title: j995229944
g.text: ok! I do love a wish guardian ^_^

g.title: j1592080673
g.text: This next wish will be better anyway :P

g.title: j4048031943
g.text: Whatever happened, I think it's cool that you're making a wish for yourself. Turning it into something happy.

g.title: j3177569475
g.text: I just thought that time might be better spent on me.

g.title: j2618106751
g.text: Oh... Okay, yes it did. My bad.

g.title: j3198449339
g.text: I think I'm beginning to understand you a lot better.

g.title: j2890927064
g.text: I'm just glad you're doing what makes you happy.

g.title: j2851099082
g.text: Next time I see you folding those cranes, I'll have a whole new appreciation.

g.title: j226510800
g.text: I've gotta run, but I'll be sending you energy for all that crane-folding.

g.title: j4057835468
g.text: if this is a joke, I don't find it very funny

g.title: j3561896432
g.text: nah I just wear cool shades

g.title: j2771628271
g.text: ^_^ ur making my heart feel very full

g.title: j4191230798
g.text: and next time I see you seeing me fold cranes, I'll have an appreciation for ur appreciation heehee

g.title: j475092655
g.text: wow! I can feel ur energy flowing through the cosmos already <3

g.title: j1732866923
g.text: Hey, I appreciate you telling me about your cranes.

g.title: j2721614444
g.text: hey, it was cool of u to show interest :)
